  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>The target is plagued with thoughts of their past failings, or what they may have forgotten. Did they leave the stove on? They make a Will saving throw at the start of their turn for as long as this spell endures.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The spell ends.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes @Damage[1d6[mental]] damage.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 1}, losing an action this turn. The creature takes @Damage[2d6[mental]] damage.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is slowed 1 for as long as the spell endures without further saving throws. The creature takes 2d6 mental damage.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The spell can target another creature within range.</p><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The range of the spell increases by 30 feet.</p><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> Increase the damage by [[/r 1d6]].</p>",
